OL,3,CNine places across UK to battle it out
OL,4,Cfor UK City of Culture title
OL,6,FBlackpool has made the long list of
OL,7,Fplaces that could become UK City of
OL,8,FCulture 2029.
OL,10,FThe competition recognises places with
OL,11,Fa strong cultural offer and gives them
OL,12,Fthe chance to secure significant
OL,13,Finvestment, boost tourism and create
OL,14,Fnew job opportunities.
OL,16,FEight locations are in the running for
OL,17,Fthe 2029 title, alongside Blackpool:
OL,18,FInverness-Highland, Ipswich,
OL,19,FMiddlesbrough, Milton Keynes,
OL,20,FPortsmouth, Sheffield, Swindon and
OL,21,FWrexham.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/11
