OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773857158
OL,3,CNine places across UK to battle it out
OL,4,Cfor UK City of Culture title
OL,6,FDespite being dubbed 'City of
OL,7,FCulture', four of the nine locations
OL,8,Fon the long list are towns.
OL,10,FEach longlisted place will receive
OL,11,F#60,000 to support the development of
OL,12,Ftheir full bid, up from #40,000 in the
OL,13,Fprevious competition.
OL,15,FThe winning location will receive a
OL,16,F#10 million prize to help deliver a
OL,17,Fyear-long programme of cultural events.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/11
