OL,3,CNine places across UK to battle it out
OL,4,Cfor UK City of Culture title
OL,6,FThe three most impressive bids from
OL,7,Fplaces that reach the shortlist but
OL,8,Fare not selected as the winner will
OL,9,Freceive #125,000 each to help them to
OL,10,Ftake forward elements of their bid.
OL,12,FCllr Lynn Williams, Leader of
OL,13,FBlackpool Council:
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
