PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773857158
OL,3,CNine places across UK to battle it out
OL,4,Cfor UK City of Culture title
OL,6,F"For far too long, opportunity has not
OL,7,Fbeen shared equally across the
OL,8,Fcountry. The UK City of Culture and
OL,9,Fnew UK Town of Culture competitions
OL,10,Frecognise the enormous contributions
OL,11,Fmade by communities all over the UK
OL,12,Fwho are all part of the story of who
OL,13,Fwe are as a nation. "I look forward to
OL,14,Fseeing what the nine longlisted places
OL,15,Fhave in store as they progress in the
OL,16,Fcompetition. I also urge any towns
OL,17,Fthinking about entering the UK Town of
OL,18,FCulture competition to seize this
OL,19,Fopportunity and get involved. It's a
OL,20,Fchance to show the country what makes
OL,21,Fthem unique and shine a spotlight on
OL,22,Ftheir cultural offer, enriching the
OL,23,Flives of local people."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@UOUD@WO]
