OL,3,CNine places across UK to battle it out
OL,4,Cfor UK City of Culture title
OL,6,FBlackpool's relationship with culture
OL,7,Fis full of variety.
OL,9,FFrom Showtown Museum, which celebrates
OL,10,Fthe town's iconic history, to the
OL,11,FGrundy Art Gallery a National
OL,12,FPortfolio Organisation presenting
OL,13,Fcontemporary work from national
OL,14,Fpartners alongside talent rooted in
OL,15,FBlackpool itself.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
