CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773857158
OL,3,CNine places across UK to battle it out
OL,4,Cfor UK City of Culture title
OL,6,FThe town also hosts major
OL,7,Finternational events such as World
OL,8,FDance Championships, through to
OL,9,Fcommunity led arts and culture
OL,10,Fprogrammes delivered in local
OL,11,Fneighbourhoods.
OL,13,FIn addition to the 150th anniversary
OL,14,Fof the Blackpool Illuminations, 2029
OL,15,Fmarks 135 years since the opening of
OL,16,FThe Blackpool Tower and the Blackpool
OL,17,FGrand Theatre, while Blackpool Winter
OL,18,FGardens will celebrate its 150th
OL,19,Fanniversary in 2028.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/11
