OL,3,CNine places across UK to battle it out
OL,4,Cfor UK City of Culture title
OL,6,FWhile not technically a city,
OL,7,FBlackpool is the 45th largest place in
OL,8,Fthe UK, with a population of 141,500
OL,9,Fand a visitor economy valued at #2bn,
OL,10,Fwhich meets the bidding criteria for
OL,11,Fboth competitions.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
