CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1773857158
OL,3,CNine places across UK to battle it out
OL,4,Cfor UK City of Culture title
OL,6,FThe City of Culture runs every four
OL,7,Fyears and was previously held in
OL,8,FBradford in 2025. During that year
OL,9,Fthey hosted over 5,000 events for
OL,10,Flocal people and visitors to enjoy.,
OL,11,Fover 75% of which were free. The year
OL,12,Finvolved over 650 local artists and
OL,13,Fresulted in capital investment for
OL,14,Fmore than 30 local cultural
OL,15,Forganisations. It also led to
OL,16,Fincreased opportunities for local
OL,17,Fpeople to get involved with events,
OL,18,Fwith over 87,000 residents taking part
OL,19,Fin key projects throughout the year.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/11
